
Quoted from the Avon website

Avon, the company for women, is a leading global beauty company with over $8 billion in annual revenue. As the worlds largest direct seller, Avon markets to women in well over 100 countries through over five million independent Avon Sales Representatives, who earn more than $3 billion annually. Avon has more than one billion annual Customer transactions.

By the end of 2006, total Avon philanthropy worldwide will have raised and awarded more than $500 million for initiatives and organizations of vital importance to women. Voted a most trusted brand on three continents, Avon was also selected by Businessweek as one of The Top 100 global Brands and honored as one of Fortune magazines 50 Best companies for Minorities.
